  <div class="" style="background-color: #6667AB; color: white; font-size: 20px; letter-spacing: .2rem; text-align: center; display: flex; justify-content: center;">
    
    <br>
    
    VISIONARY / DESIGNER / PROGRAMMER
    
    <br>
    <br>
    
    On the surface, art and science seem like oil and water.
    <br>
    But these seemingly polar opposite fields actually complement each other.
    
    <br>
    <br>
    
    They convey abstract ideas in concrete ways, challenge people to see things in different angles,
    <br>
    and lead to the creation of new knowledge.
    
    <br>
    <br>
    
    They even impact culture and society individually, and even of greater magnitude when fused together.
    <br>
    I realized that to make changes in this world requires visionary leadership and ingenuity.
    
    <br>
    <br>
    
    Through my works, I hope to not only dispel the negative stereotypes associated with art and science,
    <br>
    but to also promote inclusivity in them - especially for minority groups.
    
    <br>
    <br>
    
  </div>
  
